title: Should we buy a Jenny Noun for max 130 E?
body:
As discussed on Discord, I would like to propose to buy a female Noun
What is a noun?
The Nouns DAO project holds a single auction every day, forever. Each auction is for a  character called a Noun. Nouns are colorful pictures of pixelated, block-like figures. The winner of the Noun is granted ownership of the NFT, but also gains access to the DAO.
The purchase of a Noun offers great marketing opportunities. First of all because of the auction itself but also because the DAO has big marketing plans. 
All revenue from the day's winning bid goes into a treasury, which members of the DAO have control over through their votes. In addition, every 10th noun is for the DAO itself. Each Noun equals one vote in the DAO. The vault is very large and organisations like flamingo DOA are on board. 
Based on bids from the last week I would ask for a budget 
between 110 - 130 E

https://nouns.wtf/
www.nouns.com
